      <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex61122023-09-131" status="finalized" ana="corpusmd:colophon"><milestone unit="section" n="Colophon (77b4-78a8) pp.265-266"/><lb n="77b4"/>
         <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4895">bstan pa rgyas pa rgyan gyi nyi 'od</rs> <lb n="77b5"/> 'di || mthong bas skal ldan dga' ba bskyed pa dang || dam pa rnams kyi sku <lb n="77b6"/> drin dran bya'i phyir || <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4006">bcom ldan ral gri</rs>s legs par bkod pa yin || <lb n="77b7"/> 
         <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4895">bstan pa <choice><orig>rgyas pa rgyas pa</orig><reg>rgyas pa</reg></choice> rgyan gyi nyi 'od</rs> ces bya ba × <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4006">mang du thos pa'i dge slong 
         <lb n="77b8"/> <abbr>bcom ldan</abbr> ral gri</rs>s sbyar ba × rdzogs so || </seg>
         <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex61122023-09-13-102" status="finalized" ana="corpusmd:colophon"><milestone unit="section" n="Colophon (77b4-78a8) pp.265-266"/>
         ding sang thub bstan <pb n="78a"/><lb n="78a1"/> <rs type="place" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5559">gangs ri'i khrod</rs> 'dir dar || dar pa'i chos grangs mdo' rgyud bstan <lb n="78a2"/> bcos rnams || rnam dag ji bzhin mkhyen pa'i bla chen mchog | <lb n="78a3"/> mchog gyur <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4006">dpa' ldan ral gri</rs>'i bka' la 'dud || zhus+ho || dge'o || <lb n="78a4"/> sa mtha'i dge slong <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5098">dge 'dun bzang po</rs> ngas <note type="editorial">The BDRC reads "dpang", but looking at how the letters are generally written in that page the first letter looks more like a “nga” and the second more like a “sa” the third could be a tsheg. After the first “dge'o” all the sentence are 9 syllables long.</note> || thub bstan sgor zhugs sgo <lb n="78a5"/> gsum chos dang bstun || bla ma'i gsung bzhin gsung rabs mang du <lb n="78a6"/> mnyan || de don nyams blang dog chen grub par bsngo || laM lta ma || <lb n="78a7"/> || dpe 'di <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5842"><abbr>slob dpon</abbr> zhang</rs> gis <rs type="place" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5541">nyang stod</rs> nas gdan drangs nas <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4070"><abbr>blo gros</abbr> seng ge</rs>s <lb n="78a8"/> <rs type="place" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:5697">brag dkar</rs> du shing phag ma <abbr>bris so</abbr> <note type="editorial">"shing" is unclear.</note> || 1 <abbr>zhus so</abbr> || dag go | dge'o |</seg>
